<br>
There's a mafia-type guild called Denied on Mourning that Morokryst, my guild, has a very uneasy alliance with. I think it's all a matter of who's going to backstab who first...but that's what makes the whole thing intriguing. <br>
<br>
SB also has an interesting way of preventing twinking...mobs can drop really sweet items, but you have to have a skill at 100% to use them, which means you have to gain levels and invest training points. Even though I got an imperial breastplate at lvl 20, I'm still unable to wear it at lvl 38, although I think there is a way to cheat that...<br>
<br>
